{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"04358a1d2a","title":"在八评苏共中央的公开信稿上加写的两段话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4898e7a00f","index":0,"year":1964,"month":3,"day":17,"articleId":"04358a1d2a"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bfa9ca15d","name":"宣言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/46-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji46":{"comments":[{"id":"bd4a51191b","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"04358a1d2a","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"赫鲁晓夫，当时任苏共中央第一书记、苏联部长会议主席。"}],"contents":[{"id":"8ee78c72c9","type":"title","text":"在八评苏共中央的公开信稿上加写的两段话！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"04358a1d2a"},{"id":"bd4a51191b","type":"paragraph","text":"本文想讨论一个大家都熟悉的、很出名的问题，这就是所请和平过渡”问题。这个问题之所以出名，弄得大家都注意起来，是由于赫鲁晓夫在苏共第二十次代表大会上提了出来，在苏共第二十二次代表大会上用纲领的形式加以系统化，以其修正主义的观点，反对马克思列宁主义的观点。一九六三年七月十四日苏共中央的公开信，又重弹这个老调","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"04358a1d2a"},{"id":"c92efc1ebe","type":"paragraph","text":"S","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"04358a1d2a"},{"id":"45a7fd86f7","type":"paragraph","text":"为此原故，我们要写这篇文章，以比过去更加清楚的语言，回答修正主义者。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"04358a1d2a"},{"id":"615704272f","type":"paragraph","text":"[I]八评苏共中央的公开信以《无产阶级革命和赫鲁晓夫修正主义》为题，在1964年3月31日《人民日报》和《红旗》杂志1964年第六期发表。本篇一写在这篇文章送审稿前言部分的开头：本篇二写在送审福前言部分的末尾。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"04358a1d2a"}],"page":{"id":"a49a6fa5d3","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"04358a1d2a","start":290,"end":290}}}},"__N_SSG":true}